{"type":null,"faqId":49473,"title":"播放音乐","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p7{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.19722222in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p8{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p9{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.td1{width:0.82708335in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.td2{width:4.6854167in;padding-start:0.075in;padding-end:0.075in;border-bottom:thin solid black;border-left:thin solid black;border-right:thin solid black;border-top:thin solid black;}\n.r1{keep-together:always;}\n.t1{table-layout:fixed;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"播放音乐\"XE \"播放歌曲\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189256\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“音乐”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>选择一个类别。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击要播放的音乐。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>后续处理</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击正在播放的音乐，进入播放主界面，可进行更多操作。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189257\" style=\"width:3.0in;height:3.0in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189258\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>左右滑动可在专辑封面、播放列表和歌词之间进行切换。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span class=\"s3\">  </span><span>点击可进行更多操作，如调节播放音量、打开选项菜单等。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189259\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>更多操作。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"r1\">\n<td class=\"td1\">\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189260\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</td><td class=\"td2\">\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>控制音乐播放。</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p8\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189261\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p9\">\n<span>播放音乐时，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189262\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”</span><span class=\"s2\">主屏键</span><span>可退出播放界面，此时音乐将在后台播放。若要返回音乐播放界面，请打开通知面板，点击正在播放的音乐。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1089,"faqType":"音乐与视频","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5217","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Music-Video","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1447294368000,"seriesProductName":"KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00","visitedTimes":51,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}